{{zh-forms|[[百闻不如一见]]|[[百]][[聞]][[不如]][[一]][[見]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: băi wén bùrú yī jiàn
===Etymology===
Literally: Hearing something one hundred times is not as good as seeing it once.
===Proverb===
# Seeing is believing.

